[FACE MASKS FOR WOMEN MEN]Product includes 12 different colors masks for women men. The masks are made of cotton material, 3-layer structure, non-woven in the middle and cotton-polyester blend in the outer layer, color in black, gray, burgundy, blue, brown, rose, purple etc.

[ADJUSTABLE NOSE LINE AND CHIN PAD] Configured with an adjustable noseband strip that allows you to freely adjust the width and fit, the skin-friendly cotton wraps around the noseband strip so you don't feel constricted and prevents the mask from slipping off. A chin pad is set up at the chin to fit most women's faces, preventing air from getting in through the chin and ensuring a good fit.

[ADJUSTABLE EAR CORDS] Adjustable buckles are set at the ear ropes on both sides of the mask, so you can freely adjust the buckle position when wearing it to make the mask reach your comfortable effect. After using the adjustable ear rope, the lanyard will not rub your ears due to the suitable elasticity, and the lightness of the mask will make your experience more comfortable.

[WASHABLE AND REUSABLE] Unlike disposabl, cotton masks are more environmentally friendly and beautiful. Machine washable and hand washable, can be dried and air-dried. 12 packs are easy for you to wear during the week. You can give these as gifts to your family, parents, sister and other friends as gifts. Reusable and washable masks make your life more convenient.

[3-LAYER MASK WITH FILTER POCKET] 3 layers of fabric combined for more safety. The fabric is mainly made of cotton, which is more breathable and lightweight. The filter pocket is added on the inner side, which can be put into the filter, which can resist car exhaust, pollen, dust, etc.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I like these masks
reviews.reviewText: They are easy to wear.I feel safe after I insert the disposable filter.I like the fact that the filter can enter on both sides, it is easy to pull through and stabilize.They are colorful, so they can match what I am wearing and I still feel pretty.They are good for at least 3 cleanings, and it's a lot of masks so I don't have to restock too often.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Masks to Go With Outfits
reviews.reviewText: So far I love these masks. They are comfortable and look better than the usual paper masks. Enjoy the variety of colors. They have an inset to put in a filter, and the ear straps are adjustable along with a flexible wire for the bridge of the nose. All of this allows for a snug fit. Haven't washed any so far unsure how they will do in the wash. If they do okay, I would consider purchasing another set.

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Item is not really large
reviews.reviewText: The build on it looks good. The material feels soft on the skin. But the size was not large for men. It may be large for Women but it is not large for Men.This is one of the problems with attempting to find mask online. The details are not as clear and concise to make the purchase a easy process.The product also has what appears to be slots for filter inserts. Being that I did not want to use them since they was small I did not wash them nor place them on my face for fit / comfort check.These mask should fit medium face size of men. Maybe teenager roughly.No complaints on the quality as I could not confirm or validate anything.
